<h2> Definition </h2>

This sentence pattern is used to convey the speaker's subjective conjecture based on information
the speaker directly perceives. The speaker bases his judgement on first-hand reliable
information, usually visual information.

</br>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<ol>
<li>
