    @HI{{@KJ{{matter^happenstance}}no<strong>you desu</strong> ne. @KT{{patoka-}}to
    @KJ{{salvation^hurry^car}}ga @KJ{{come}}te imasuyo.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    It looks like there has been an accident. A patrol car and ambulance are there.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
    @HI{{sekimo @KJ{{exit}}rushi, @KJ{{head}}mo @KJ{{pain}}i. doumo kaze wo hita<strong>you desu</strong>.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    I have a cough and a headache. It looks like I've caught a cold.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>

